==== How to Stop and Restart Jenkins:
======================================

     sudo systemctl daemon-reload (if you changed any config files)
       sudo systemctl restart jenkins
         sudo systemctl status jenkins 
We have to stop the jenkins before changing the Port:
========================================
sudo systemctl stop jenkins
 vi /lib/systemcd/system/jenkins.service    If this doesn't work then try this        sudo systemctl edit jenkins
   change environment port to: 8843
